                            <p class="paragraph-content">The biggest challenge for businesses in the era of modern technology is disrupting their business processes or losing to new competitors that are unique and advanced in technology. The role of information technology is increasing nowadays, businesses are required to adopt digital technology to meet consumer expectation and ensure their business presence going forward. This digital distribution brings big changes to the business. </p>
                            <p class="paragraph-content">Businesses are currently trying to reform how their business processes work and capture more consumers. The following are some of the priorities of companies to improve their business excellence in the midst of a business environment that continues to be distorted with technology:</p>
                            <div class="list">
                                <li><p>1. Transform into industry 4.0</p></li>
